song.englishname: The Dark Side Of Indoor Track Meets

english.segment1: Such fluorescent, you must wonder how I sleep. Shaking spells end, as the cuts lined up my knees
english.segment2: I guess I'm weightless as I tape my eyelids up. But now I wonder that I may have ran too far
english.segment3: Watch me float by, a bending, arched and sweeping sight. Now play it backwards, and I swear you will see me misty-eyed
english.segment4: If there's complications, pull the plug out. Pull the plug out
